    "description": "Are you a skilled Backend Developer looking for your next big career move? ISRO Advisory Limited in Vadodara offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout ISRO Advisory Limited:\nISRO Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ISRO Advisory Limited!",
